Historically, that's insignificant.

194
00:21:20,354 --> 00:21:22,346
As a U.S. example,

195
00:21:22,564 --> 00:21:25,019
50,000 died
at the Battle of Gettysburg.

196
00:21:25,233 --> 00:21:33,939
What is significant,
as my old prof said,

197
00:21:35,409 --> 00:21:37,697
