the heart of the Empire.

198
00:21:37,912 --> 00:21:40,699
In previous conflicts- Korea,
Vietnam, the Gulf War

199
00:21:40,915 --> 00:21:46,833
the Empire managed to keep the barbarians
outside its gates, its borders

200
